# Command line operations

Launch geco from the command line: `java -jar gecoXXXX.jar`

Options:
- `--startdir <aDirectoryWithData>`: opens Geco directly on the selected stage, without showing the launcher
- `--leisure`: enable the leisure mode for the LiveMap, showing simplified data and no race time for leisure runners who should not be timed

Other programs accessible from the command line:
- `java -jar gecoXXX.jar valmo.geco.GecoPools <aDirectoryWithData>`: runs the [pool merger](quals.html) in batch mode
- `java -jar gecoXXX.jar valmo.geco.live.GecoLive`: opens the GecoLive server for [animation](live.html)